{"abstract":[{"text":"Atomically releases ","type":"text"},{"code":"mutex","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and waits until ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cond"},{"text":" is signalled.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"When this function returns, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"mutex"},{"type":"text","text":" is locked again and owned by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"calling thread.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/CondProtocol"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/condprotocol\/wait(mutex:)"]}],"metadata":{"title":"wait(mutex:)","externalID":"s:4GLib12CondProtocolPAAE4wait5mutexyqd___tAA05MutexC0Rd__lF","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GLib","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"wait"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"MutexT","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"mutex","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"MutexT","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/CondProtocol\/wait(mutex:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"wait","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"MutexT","kind":"genericParameter"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"text":"mutex","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MutexT"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MutexT","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MutexProt